Introduction

Sihoon is a South Korean singer under Haeirum Entertainment. He is the leader and main rapper of the boy group F.able.

On March 22, 2024, it was revealed that Sihoon will be re-debuting in a new 3-member group called Enphaze with Jeong and Junhyoung.
